message: Add change log and FAQ link to documentation

Fix Gradle tests on Linux (refs #5184):
Build still won't work on Linux, so if launching the tests from Gradle, comment out the line "dependsOn assemble"
Support Android Studio version 3.0 (closes #5180), and move demo and product projects to that version
Change minimum API level from 9 to 15 (closes #5282)
Add build variant for demo app
Add stand-alone console app in public repository (closes #5344)
Don't include build machine packages in post-install `pip check`
Make update_public.sh also update Chaquopy version numbers and create chaquopy-hello commits
Update `target` build process after testing in clean environment
Rearrange and update READMEs  /  Simplify pkgtest build.gradle
Update piptest to Android Gradle plugin 7.0.2 and Java 11
Stop updating separate demo app repository
